OL,3,C'Deeply failed by system she devoted
OL,4,Cher life to': Nurse dies after
OL,5,Cmisdiagnosis
OL,7,FITV Granada Reports journalist Anna
OL,8,FYoussef was in court for the inquest's
OL,9,Fconclusion
OL,11,FA nurse who died days after being
OL,12,Fmisdiagnosed with indigestion could
OL,13,Fstill be alive if she had been
OL,14,Fproperly diagnosed and given emergency
OL,15,Fsurgery, an inquest has found.
OL,17,FPaula Ivers was found dead by her nine-
OL,18,Fyear-old daughter after being sent
OL,19,Fhome and instructed to buy Gaviscon
OL,20,Ffrom Tameside Hospital, Greater
OL,21,FManchester, in March 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
