FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781722095
OL,3,C'Deeply failed by system she devoted
OL,4,Cher life to': Nurse dies after
OL,5,Cmisdiagnosis
OL,7,FA coroner has now ruled Paula's death
OL,8,Fwas "contributed to by neglect" after
OL,9,Fdoctors failed to spot the mum had
OL,10,Fsuffered an aortic tear - which
OL,11,Fultimately led to a fatal cardiac
OL,12,Farrest.
OL,14,FPaula's sister Lesley read a statement
OL,15,Foutside the coroner's court following
OL,16,Fher sister's inquest conclusion
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781722095
OL,3,C'Deeply failed by system she devoted
OL,4,Cher life to': Nurse dies after
OL,5,Cmisdiagnosis
OL,7,FHer family say Paula - who had been a
OL,8,Fpaediatric nurse for more than 24
OL,9,Fyears - was let down by the very
OL,10,Fservice she had dedicated her career
OL,11,Fto.
OL,13,F"She was deeply failed by very system
OL,14,Fto which she devoted her life," her
OL,15,Fsister Lesley Ivers, who is also a
OL,16,Fnurse, said.
OL,18,F"Paula deserved far better, both as
OL,19,Fpatient and professional who gave so
OL,20,Fmuch to others.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781722095
OL,3,C'Deeply failed by system she devoted
OL,4,Cher life to': Nurse dies after
OL,5,Cmisdiagnosis
OL,7,F"Her daughter has been left utterly
OL,8,Fdevastated and traumatised by her
OL,9,Fmother's death, the impact on her, and
OL,10,Fall of us as a family is something we
OL,11,Fwill carry forever."
OL,13,FDuring a two day inquest South
OL,14,FManchester Coroners' Court, in
OL,15,FStockport, heard the 47-year-old had
OL,16,Fgone to the accident and emergency
OL,17,Fdepartment after experiencing crushing
OL,18,Fchest pains which she described to her
OL,19,Fpartner as being worse than childbirth.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781722095
OL,3,C'Deeply failed by system she devoted
OL,4,Cher life to': Nurse dies after
OL,5,Cmisdiagnosis
OL,7,FAfter being triaged in A&E Paula was
OL,8,Fsent to the Same Day Emergency Care
OL,9,FUnit which treats patients assessed as
OL,10,Fnot requiring hospital admission.
OL,12,FShe was seen by a junior doctor where
OL,13,Fshe was asked for the first time about
OL,14,Fher family history and told medics her
OL,15,Ffather had died from a cardiac arrest
OL,16,Fwhen he was just 45.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781722095
OL,3,C'Deeply failed by system she devoted
OL,4,Cher life to': Nurse dies after
OL,5,Cmisdiagnosis
OL,7,FThe inquest was told Paula's blood
OL,8,Ftests and ECG were normal and despite
OL,9,Fbeing given a chest X-ray she was not
OL,10,Fgiven a CT scan, which is the most
OL,11,Fcommon way to diagnose an aortic
OL,12,Fdissection.
OL,14,FHer case was then discussed with the
OL,15,Funit's clinical lead - who had only
OL,16,Fbeen a fully qualified GP for just
OL,17,Fover a year - where she was diagnosed
OL,18,Fwith acid reflux.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781722095
OL,3,C'Deeply failed by system she devoted
OL,4,Cher life to': Nurse dies after
OL,5,Cmisdiagnosis
OL,7,FCoroner Christopher Morris told the
OL,8,Finquest he believed because Aortic
OL,9,FDissection is quite rare, and because
OL,10,Fboth doctors were "relatively
OL,11,Finexperienced", it did not occur to
OL,12,Fthem it could be a cause.
OL,14,FInstead Paula was told to buy a bottle
OL,15,Fof Gaviscon and sent home.
OL,17,FA post mortem examination revealed she
OL,18,Fdied from an aortic dissection, a time-
OL,19,Fcritical medical emergency caused by a
OL,20,Ftear in the aorta.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781722095
OL,3,C'Deeply failed by system she devoted
OL,4,Cher life to': Nurse dies after
OL,5,Cmisdiagnosis
OL,7,FRecording a narrative conclusion
OL,8,Fcontributed to by neglect the coroner
OL,9,Falso said he would also be issuing
OL,10,Fprevention of future deaths reports to
OL,11,Fthe NHS Trust and the Health Secretary.
OL,13,FNicola Ashton, a Senior Associate
OL,14,FSolicitor for Irwin Mitchell, and the
OL,15,Ffamily's lawyer said the family want
OL,16,Fto "ensure meaningful change comes
OL,17,Ffrom Paula's death".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781722095
OL,3,C'Deeply failed by system she devoted
OL,4,Cher life to': Nurse dies after
OL,5,Cmisdiagnosis
OL,7,F"Today's finding of neglect, and the
OL,8,FCoroner issuing two Prevention of
OL,9,FFuture Deaths reports, is deeply
OL,10,Fsignificant," she said.
OL,12,F"It confirms the family's concerns
OL,13,Fand, they hope, will lead to real
OL,14,Fchange so no other family has to go
OL,15,Fthrough this. The family have shown
OL,16,Fimmense strength throughout this
OL,17,Fprocess.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1781722095
OL,3,C'Deeply failed by system she devoted
OL,4,Cher life to': Nurse dies after
OL,5,Cmisdiagnosis
OL,7,F"Their priority has always been to
OL,8,Fseek answers and ensure that
OL,9,Fmeaningful change comes from Paula's
OL,10,Fdeath. We will continue to support
OL,11,Fthem as the inquest concludes and as
OL,12,Fthe related civil proceedings
OL,13,Fprogress."
OL,15,FA Tameside and Glossop Integrated Care
OL,16,FNHS Foundation Trust spokesperson said
OL,17,Fit accepted the coroner's findings.
OL,19,F"Our thoughts are first and foremost
OL,20,Fwith Paula's loved ones during this
OL,21,Fvery difficult time," it said.
OL,26,@uD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
