OL,3,C'Deeply failed by system she devoted
OL,4,Cher life to': Nurse dies after
OL,5,Cmisdiagnosis
OL,7,F"We accept the coroner's findings and
OL,8,Foffer our deepest apologies that Paula
OL,9,Fdid not receive the standard of care
OL,10,Fshe should have."
OL,12,FWant more on the issues effecting the
OL,13,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,14,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,15,Four region.
